:::{{A|VO chapter2 11 yanqing 104.ogg}} '''Yanqing:''' I was planning to take Miss March and Yunli to Stargazer Navalia to see the Skysplitter up close, but we stumbled upon a group of suspicious foxians carrying official identities.
:::{{tx}}
::;(Return to previous option selection)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's your plan now?
:::{{A|VO chapter2 11 yanqing 108.ogg}} '''Yanqing:''' The borisin traveled all the way here to infiltrate the Luofu and attempt to rescue their leader with a crafty scheme... This is completely unlike them. To be honest, it reminds me of what the Disciples of Sanctus Medicus did during the Ambrosial Arbor Crisis.
:::{{tx}}
::;(Return to previous option selection)
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Those tourists over there are talking about you...
