::{{tx}}
:{{A|VO chapter2 11 feixiao 102.ogg}} '''Feixiao:''' You may be tiny in stature, but your ambition matches that of the Yaoqing's warriors.
:{{A|VO chapter2 11 yanqing 116.ogg}} '''Yanqing:''' Hey, this has nothing to do with my height.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What brings you here, General?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I thought all the generals were on the move already?
:{{A|VO chapter2 11 feixiao 103.ogg}} '''Feixiao:''' Yes, I suggested to Yanqing that we find a place to have a decent meal. A hunter must be well-fed before "the hunt."
:{{tx}}
